trans-unit.source: Represents the key for an entry in a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 表示中的条目的键<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: When caching a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken> there are two indexes required.
trans-unit.target: 在缓存时<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken>有两个所需的索引。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: One is the context ID, represented by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.ContextId%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, that is unique across all session tokens.
trans-unit.target: 一个是上下文 ID，由表示<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.ContextId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性中所有会话令牌都是唯一的。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.ContextId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The other is the key generation, represented by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.KeyGeneration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, which is unique within a session token.
trans-unit.target: 另一种是密钥生成，由表示<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.KeyGeneration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性，它是在会话令牌中唯一。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.KeyGeneration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: When a session token is issued it has only a context ID.
trans-unit.target: 会话令牌颁发时具有仅上下文 id。

trans-unit.source: When the session token is renewed, the key generation is added.
trans-unit.target: 续订的会话令牌时，将添加密钥生成。

trans-unit.source: After renewal, the renewed session token is uniquely identifiable via the context ID and key generation.
trans-unit.target: 续订后，续订的会话令牌的唯一地标识通过上下文 ID 和密钥生成。

trans-unit.source: Objects of type SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey are used as the indexes to the session token cache.
trans-unit.target: 类型 SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey 的对象用作会话令牌缓存的索引。

trans-unit.source: An index will always have a valid <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.ContextId%2A> property specified, but the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.KeyGeneration%2A> property may be `null`, depending on whether the token has been renewed.
trans-unit.target: 索引将始终有一个有效<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.ContextId%2A>属性指定，但<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.KeyGeneration%2A>属性可以是`null`，取决于是否续订令牌。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.KeyGeneration%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.ContextId%2A>

trans-unit.source: There is also an optional <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.EndpointId%2A> which gives the endpoint to which the token is scoped.
trans-unit.target: 此外还有一个可选<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.EndpointId%2A>这将给予为作用域令牌的终结点。</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey.EndpointId%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCacheKey"></xref>类。

trans-unit.source: The endpoint ID to which the cache entry is scoped.
trans-unit.target: 为作用域的缓存项的终结点 ID。

trans-unit.source: This is should be the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.EndpointId%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the cached token.
trans-unit.target: 这是应的值<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.EndpointId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>的缓存的令牌的属性。

trans-unit.source: The context ID of the cache entry.
trans-unit.target: 缓存项的上下文 ID。

trans-unit.source: This is should be the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.ContextId%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the cached token.
trans-unit.target: 这是应的值<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.ContextId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>的缓存的令牌的属性。

trans-unit.source: The key generation of the cache entry.
trans-unit.target: 密钥生成的缓存项。

trans-unit.source: This is should be the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.KeyGeneration%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property of the cached token.
trans-unit.target: 这是应的值<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityToken.KeyGeneration%2A?displayProperty=fullName>的缓存的令牌的属性。

trans-unit.source: This value is available when the token is renewed.
trans-unit.target: 当续订令牌后，此值才可用。

trans-unit.source: It will be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> when caching a new token.
trans-unit.target: 它将是<xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>时缓存新令牌。

trans-unit.source: Gets the context ID for the cache key.
trans-unit.target: 获取缓存密钥的上下文 ID。

trans-unit.source: Gets the Endpoint ID to which this cache entry is scoped.

trans-unit.source: The Endpoint ID to which this cache entry is scoped.

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>指定的对象是否与当前的缓存键; 相同否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示是否可以执行索引比较时忽略密钥生成。
